<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565695>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Scanning electron micrographs of Orec- toderus obliquus (male). A. Head and thorax (lateral view). B. Metathoracic scent-gland evaporatory area (lateral view). C. Pretarsus (frontal view); detail of the tibial comb. D. Setae on hemelytra, detail of microstructure. E. Pygophore (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4565695/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565697>
